<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4567356>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Amphibolips quercuspomiformis comb. nov.: (A) habitus; (B) head in dorsal view; (C) Head and mesosoma in lateral view (the arrow points to the speculum); (D) Head in frontal view; (E) Mesosoma in dorsal view; (F) Metasoma in lateral view, detail of micropunctures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4567356/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4567358>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. (A–D) Amphibolips quercuspomiformis comb. nov.: (A) Forewing; (B) Antennae; (C) Metatarsi and tarsal claws; (D) Tarsal claws. (E) Amphibolips turulli n. sp.: (E) Tarsal claws." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4567358/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4567376>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Galls. (A–D) A. quercuspomiformis comb. nov.: (A) mature gall, (B) dry gall, (C–D) internal tissue, larval cells signaled (white arrow); (E–G) A. bassae n. sp.: (E) dry gall, (F) internal tissue, (G) mature gall; (H–I) A. tarasco: (H) dry gall, (I) internal tissue; (J) A. kinseyi n. sp., dry gall." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4567376/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

